Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您提问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.07,0:01:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神纳小姐已经做社长秘书五年了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,业务内容主要都是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在外资汽车厂商工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要业务内容是管理社长的日程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有公司内外衔接等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我本职是社长助手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但根据实际情况 我也会履行员工职责以保持员工与社长之间沟通顺畅 我认为这是我应尽的义务之一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:01:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也经常会出现要求我随机应变地去处理的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我认为作为判断事态的根据 与员工之间的沟通也是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里需要秘书具备怎样的处理能力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.44,0:02:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何巧妙应对上司的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要的只是对生意有帮助的任性 保留正确意见摒弃错误
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为秘书这份工作其实就是服务业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外 还应该彻底履行保密义务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在社长身边工作的话 经常会接触到普通员工无法知晓的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不慎地将那些秘密泄露给想知道的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能会酿成大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为防止这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对重要机密需要守口如瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请谈谈这份工作对于您的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭兴趣参加各种研讨会 总之要扩展各种各样商业知识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 有那么多生意经营在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然有机会在一起工作 必须向他们积极学习
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次社长对我说“你能当我的秘书真是太好了”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我感到由衷的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天来是有事商量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.73,0:04:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是谈谈罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过喝一杯不介意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢好意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天请不要做别的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在生什么气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次打了你还在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次在最后我应该说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再叫我过来这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不至于..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次你几天没来 我们都很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您不要乱拍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是第一次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被全公司知道也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我会很为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要我住手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在对着哪儿说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,态度不端正的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“求求您了”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:06:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是最开始就是那种态度的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就谈泷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐能稍微忍忍就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己坐下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就该坐下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试着张开腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腿张开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,张开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.50,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的镜头 可正拍着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认真点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿可以摸摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然好久没做了 不应该更积极吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 摸到咪咪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 怎么了 不冷静了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他摸一摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奶子不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐 手感不错吧 喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起来爽吧\N我不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正脸对着镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口是心非吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉没啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍两张咪咪怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要拍 不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腿张开些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,硬邦邦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咪咪好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身都是性带感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在有感觉了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为继续摩擦下去会舒服过头 所以才叫住手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没说错吧\N不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔咪咪也不会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会很兴奋的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那试试就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才哆嗦了一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢被粗暴对待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始娇喘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娇喘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得之后我们会怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请在今天结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为会兴奋对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受够了会兴奋起来的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这种爽的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有觉得..爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让点儿让你更兴奋些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骚味儿都漂到我这儿来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你闭拢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你张开啊 要我说几次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛睁开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看把逼秀出来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着前面的镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样\N要这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快看镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我 看镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说“我是社长秘书”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我叫神纳花”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我是社长秘书”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我叫神纳花”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“今天”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我被强暴了”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭什么啊哭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭了吗\N就快要哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
